// Bohlen-Pierce — 13 notes per tritave (ratio 3:1 instead of 2:1)
// Non-octave scale, unique harmonic structure
// Note: non-terminals avoid A-G letters (BP3 parses them as notes)

@core
@controls
@alphabet.bohlen_pierce:browser
@mm:80

S -> Montee Retour Tenue

Montee -> C D E F G H J (wave:triangle, vel:80)
Retour -> J H G F E D C (vel:70)
Tenue -> C _ _ _ (vel:60)
